            <span class="bento-mock-tag brand">€79/mo</span>
            <span class="bento-mock-tag">Local Rank Tracking</span>
            <span class="bento-mock-tag brand">White-Label</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-cta">Need content + GBP? theStacc handles both <span class="arrow">→</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-card">
        <div class="bento-num">✓</div>
