      </div>
      <div class="ba-col before">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">Skip Nightwatch if</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">You need content output.</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">Three signals you need a different tool.</p>
